 {"id":"asupersync-3qv04.8.6","title":"[WASM][QA] Wire deterministic CI entrypoints and failure-triage playbooks for the wasm test stack","description":"Turn the test pyramid into reliable operational machinery: stable commands, CI entrypoints, log locations, artifact conventions, and a written failure-triage workflow. This bead should make it obvious how to run the whole Browser Edition quality stack, what evidence is expected on failure, and how to interpret the generated logs/artifacts.\n\nWithout this work, even good tests decay into tribal knowledge. With it, the browser quality story stays reproducible for both humans and future agents.","status":"in_progress","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"AzureValley","estimated_minutes":240,"created_at":"2026-03-06T15:13:58.900642161Z","created_by":"CopperForest","updated_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:33.060788460Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["ci","logging","qa","wasm"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-3qv04.8.6","depends_on_id":"asupersync-3qv04.8","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-06T15:13:58.900642161Z","created_by":"CopperForest","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"asupersync-3qv04.8.6","depends_on_id":"asupersync-3qv04.8.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-06T15:17:06.681674336Z","created_by":"CopperForest","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"asupersync-3qv04.8.6","depends_on_id":"asupersync-3qv04.8.2.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-06T15:30:30.191083015Z","created_by":"CopperForest","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"asupersync-3qv04.8.6","depends_on_id":"asupersync-3qv04.8.2.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-06T15:30:32.769139053Z","created_by":"CopperForest","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"asupersync-3qv04.8.6","depends_on_id":"asupersync-3qv04.8.2.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-06T15:30:35.318532767Z","created_by":"CopperForest","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"asupersyn